'''Lon Drasna''' was the capital city of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Dandrian]]. It was a sprawling cityport which contained [[The Watering Hole]], among other [[Cantina/Legends|cantinas]]. Many illicit [[Swoop/Legends|swoop]] races were held in the town. Nothing was said to happen in the city without [[Sti Groon]] knowing.

